p.s:
The provinces mostly coincide with the 21 counties (
län
) , the mid-level political entities .

The 290 municipalities (
kommun
) , are the bottom-level political entities , typically consisting of a town or a city , and the surrounding countryside , including small villages .

Some municipalities used to hold city (
stad
) privileges , and still style themselves as such , though there is no legal distinction .

item.s:
( Swedish :
Göteborg
) is Sweden 's largest port and industrial centre , second in population .

( Swedish :
Höga kusten
) is the most scenic area along the Norrland coast .

( Swedish :
Stockholms skärgård
) consists of islands all shapes and sizes .
